    "en": {
      "name": "Sacred Azamina",
      "effect": "Reveal 1 \"Azamina\" Fusion Monster in your Extra Deck and send 1 \"Sinful Spoils\" card from your hand and/or field to the GY for every 4 Levels the revealed monster has (if those cards are Set, reveal them), then Special Summon it. (This is treated as a Fusion Summon.) If this card is in your GY: You can target 1 \"Azamina\" monster you control or in your GY; shuffle it into the Deck, and if you do, add this card to your hand. You can only use this effect of \"Sacred Azamina\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
